289
00:18:41,538 --> 00:18:45,666
...this deplorable incident
at the Democratic National Committee."

290
00:18:45,834 --> 00:18:48,252
HOWARD:
Isn't that what you'd expect them to say?

291
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:49,461
Absolutely.

292
00:18:49,963 --> 00:18:51,046
So?

293
00:18:51,548 --> 00:18:53,716
I never asked about Watergate.

294
00:18:54,301 --> 00:18:57,386
I simply asked what were Hunt's duties
