351
00:22:05,492 --> 00:22:06,533
May I have it, please?

352
00:22:06,701 --> 00:22:08,285
- Your conclusions...
- May I have it?

353
00:22:08,453 --> 00:22:10,579
- I'm not looking for a fight.
- I'm not either.

354
00:22:10,747 --> 00:22:14,041
I'm just aware of the fact
that you've only been here nine months.

355
00:22:14,834 --> 00:22:16,543
What's that got to do with anything?

356
00:22:16,711 --> 00:22:19,338
- Been in the business since I'm 16.
