00:22:36,899 --> 00:22:38,899
is better, we'll give
yours to the desk.

364
00:22:39,067 --> 00:22:41,276
I've got Colson's name up front.

365
00:22:42,445 --> 00:22:45,489
- He was a consultant and nobody knows it.
