384
00:23:59,522 --> 00:24:02,190
Did you know Howard Hunt?

385
00:24:02,358 --> 00:24:04,776
- Didn't he work in the office?
- Yeah, I knew Howard.

386
00:24:04,944 --> 00:24:07,112
- Nice?
- He's a nice person.

387
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:10,574
He's secretive.
He's secretive but a decent man.

388
00:24:10,742 --> 00:24:14,703
Do you have any idea what he did?

389
00:24:14,871 --> 00:24:18,040
Well, the White House said
he was doing some investigative work.

390
00:24:18,207 --> 00:24:19,249
What do you say?

391
00:24:19,417 --> 00:24:21,168
[SHARON CHUCKLES]

392
00:24:21,336 --> 00:24:23,629
- He was doing investigative work.
