394
00:24:30,303 --> 00:24:31,762
- I'm not gonna...
- She warned me.

395
00:24:31,929 --> 00:24:34,723
I'm not gonna take my book out.
I'm just asking you.

396
00:24:35,391 --> 00:24:38,852
Well, the scuttlebutt for a while
was that he was investigating Kennedy.

