00:24:39,020 --> 00:24:40,395
Why?

398
00:24:40,563 --> 00:24:43,899
The White House was real paranoid
about Teddy Kennedy.

399
00:24:45,193 --> 00:24:48,445
I remember seeing a book
about Chappaquiddick on his desk.

400
00:24:48,613 --> 00:24:50,155
He was always getting material...

401
00:24:50,323 --> 00:24:53,283
...out of the White House library
and the Library of Congress.

402
00:24:53,451 --> 00:24:55,619
Anything he could find.

403
00:24:57,121 --> 00:24:58,580
WOMAN 1:
White House library.

