00:24:58,748 --> 00:25:01,083
Hi, this is Carl Bernstein,
of the Washington Post.

405
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:03,585
I was wondering
if you can remember any books...

406
00:25:03,753 --> 00:25:07,255
...that a Howard Hunt checked out
on Senator Kennedy?

407
00:25:07,423 --> 00:25:10,217
- Howard Hunt? Um...
