00:38:18,088 --> 00:38:21,007
I mean, you'd be on deep background.

565
00:38:24,052 --> 00:38:25,553
You can trust me. You know that.

566
00:38:29,391 --> 00:38:30,850
Go on.

567
00:38:33,395 --> 00:38:37,523
- Can you tell me what you know?
