568
00:38:41,737 --> 00:38:44,614
Hunt worked for Colson
at the White House.

569
00:38:45,449 --> 00:38:48,326
Hunt was investigating Kennedy
at Chappaquiddick.

570
00:38:48,494 --> 00:38:52,747
That should tell you a lot. What else?

571
00:38:53,415 --> 00:38:57,668
We're beginning to hear a lot about a
