675
00:45:27,392 --> 00:45:29,810
The man I work for
has started a reelection campaign.

676
00:45:29,978 --> 00:45:32,146
We're gonna have to
see each other tomorrow.

677
00:45:32,314 --> 00:45:34,982
No, I'm facing a deadline.
