You have a man...

2049
02:02:09,573 --> 02:02:12,909
...who's the editor of the Washington Post
by the name of Ben Bradlee.

2050
02:02:13,410 --> 02:02:18,456
I think anyone who were to honestly assess
what his political persuasions are...

2051
02:02:18,624 --> 02:02:22,418
...would, I think,
come to the conclusion quite quickly...

2052
02:02:22,586 --> 02:02:25,129
...that he is not a supporter
of President Nixon.

2053
02:02:25,589 --> 02:02:27,215
I respect the free press.

2054
02:02:27,382 --> 02:02:30,635
I don't respect the type of journalism...

2055
02:02:30,802 --> 02:02:33,179
The shabby journalism
that is being practiced...

2056
02:02:33,347 --> 02:02:34,555
...by the Washington Post.

2057
02:02:34,723 --> 02:02:39,560
All I know is that the story
that ran this morning is incorrect...

2058
02:02:39,728 --> 02:02:44,440
...and has been so stated
as being incorrect...

2059
02:02:44,608 --> 02:02:48,528
...by not only me, but by the individual
whose grand-jury...

2060
02:02:48,695 --> 02:02:52,281
Secret grand-jury testimony
they based their story on.

2061
02:02:52,449 --> 02:02:56,494
And that individual has denied
that he ever so testified.

2062
02:02:56,828 --> 02:02:58,371
ANNOUNCER:
No sooner had Ziegler finished...

2063
02:02:58,539 --> 02:03:02,124
...than the president's campaign manager,
Clark MacGregor, met with reporters.

2064
02:03:02,292 --> 02:03:05,461
MacGREGOR:
Using innuendo, third-person hearsay...

2065
02:03:05,629 --> 02:03:09,090
...unsubstantiated charges,
anonymous sources...

2066
02:03:09,258 --> 02:03:11,259
...and huge scare headlines...

2067
02:03:11,426 --> 02:03:14,387
...the Post has maliciously sought
to give the appearance...

2068
02:03:14,555 --> 02:03:17,807
...of a direct connection between
the White House and the Watergate...

2069
02:03:17,975 --> 02:03:19,767
...a charge which the Post knows...

2070
02:03:19,935 --> 02:03:23,813
...and half a dozen investigations
have found, to be false.

2071
02:03:23,981 --> 02:03:27,692
The hallmark of the Post's campaign
is hypocrisy...

2072
02:03:27,859 --> 02:03:32,321
...and its celebrated double standard
is today visible for all to see.

2073
02:03:32,489 --> 02:03:34,824
BOB: What do you mean?
- I'm not talking about Haldeman.

2074
02:03:34,992 --> 02:03:36,200
CARL: What went wrong?
- Nothing.

2075
02:03:36,368 --> 02:03:37,493
Tell us what went wrong.

2076
02:03:37,661 --> 02:03:40,580
BOB: Didn't you say the FBI had information
on Haldeman in the files?

2077
02:03:40,747 --> 02:03:43,874
We have it in the notes from
the conversation with you on the phone.

2078
02:03:44,042 --> 02:03:46,502
We have to go talk to your boss
if you don't talk.

2079
02:03:46,670 --> 02:03:49,338
JOE: What the hell are you talking about?
I'll deny everything.

2080
02:03:49,506 --> 02:03:52,675
We're just trying to find out
if we made some errors.

2081
02:03:52,843 --> 02:03:54,969
If we made a mistake,
we'll come off the story.

2082
02:03:55,137 --> 02:03:56,470
CARL:
Just tell us if we're wrong.

2083
02:03:56,638 --> 02:03:59,307
Tell us if we screwed up.
Tell us if it's wrong. Tell us...

2084
02:03:59,474 --> 02:04:00,850
I'm not talking about it.

2085
02:04:01,018 --> 02:04:04,145
I am not talking to you about Haldeman
or anybody else.

2086
02:04:04,313 --> 02:04:06,772
I can't even be seen talking
to either one of you bastards.

2087
02:04:06,940 --> 02:04:08,691
CARL: What are you afraid of?
Who got to you?

2088
02:04:08,859 --> 02:04:10,610
BOB:
Are we being set up?

2089
02:04:11,403 --> 02:04:13,279
CARL: Are we? Tell us.
BOB: Are we being set up?

2090
02:04:13,447 --> 02:04:17,992
CARL: Just tell us, we won't say anything.
- Fuck you. And fuck you.

2091
02:04:24,249 --> 02:04:26,083
BOB:
Honest to God, I just don't understand.

2092
02:04:26,251 --> 02:04:28,210
CARL:
It's in the notes.

2093
02:04:28,378 --> 02:04:32,006
"Yeah, we had another call all along.
I've got another call. I've gotta go."

2094
02:04:32,174 --> 02:04:34,842
"Did you mean Bob Haldeman?"
"Yeah, Bob Haldeman."

2095
02:04:37,387 --> 02:04:39,055
CARL:
Jesus, what was our mistake?

2096
02:04:40,057 --> 02:04:42,058
BOB:
Maybe there was no mistake.

2097
02:04:42,225 --> 02:04:46,395
CARL: Then they're just setting us up.
Then the whole thing was a setup.

2098
02:04:47,939 --> 02:04:49,815
And they just hung us.

2099
02:04:50,400 --> 02:04:53,402
HOWARD: More denunciations.
Gonna have to make a statement, Ben.

2100
02:04:53,570 --> 02:04:57,406
One senator just gave a speech
slurring us 57 times in 20 minutes.

2101
02:04:57,574 --> 02:05:00,868
I knew we had enemies,
but I didn't know we were this popular.

2102
02:05:01,536 --> 02:05:03,829
Wow, look at this.

2103
02:05:05,582 --> 02:05:08,042
My non-denial denial.

2104
02:05:16,426 --> 02:05:18,260
Fuck it, let's stand by the boys.

2105
02:05:19,429 --> 02:05:21,972
HOWARD:
Okay. Foreign?

2106
02:05:22,391 --> 02:05:24,308
All right, here's our headline.

2107
02:05:24,476 --> 02:05:27,645
Radio Hanoi reports the
United States-North Vietnam agreement...

2108
02:05:27,813 --> 02:05:30,106
...for a settlement of the Vietnam War.

2109
02:05:30,399 --> 02:05:31,440
[PHONE RINGING]

2110
02:05:31,608 --> 02:05:34,068
MAN [ON RADIO]: Artie was just saying,
in the few seconds we have left...

2111
02:05:34,236 --> 02:05:37,029
...just saying that vibrato sound
that she had then, she still has now.

2112
02:05:37,197 --> 02:05:38,239
[MUSIC PLAYING ON RADIO]

2113
02:05:38,407 --> 02:05:40,825
CARL: Woodward, what did you find out?
What did he say?

2114
02:05:40,992 --> 02:05:43,035
- What time is it?
- You fell asleep?

2115
02:05:43,203 --> 02:05:45,287
BOB:
Oh, goddamn it.

2116
02:06:08,395 --> 02:06:09,812
[BOB SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

2117
02:07:09,039 --> 02:07:10,706
DEEP THROAT:
Over here.

2118
02:07:33,897 --> 02:07:36,732
- You let Haldeman slip away.
- Yes.

2119
02:07:36,900 --> 02:07:38,984
You've done worse
than let Haldeman slip away.

2120
02:07:39,152 --> 02:07:43,030
You got people feeling sorry for him.
I didn't think that was possible.

2121
02:07:43,198 --> 02:07:44,907
In a conspiracy like this...

2122
02:07:45,075 --> 02:07:48,536
...you build from the outer edges
and you go step by step.

2123
02:07:48,703 --> 02:07:51,831
If you shoot too high and miss,
everybody feels more secure.

2124
02:07:52,707 --> 02:07:56,627
- You put the investigation back months.
- Yes, we know that.

2125
02:07:56,795 --> 02:07:59,421
And if we're wrong, we're resigning.

2126
02:08:00,674 --> 02:08:02,091
Were we wrong?

2127
02:08:04,594 --> 02:08:09,473
- You'll have to find that out, won't you?
- I'm tired of your chicken-shit games.

2128
02:08:10,767 --> 02:08:12,768
I don't want hints.

2129
02:08:12,936 --> 02:08:14,770
I need to know what you know.

2130
02:08:31,121 --> 02:08:33,956
It was a Haldeman operation.

2131
02:08:34,666 --> 02:08:38,711
The whole business was run by Haldeman,
the money, everything.

2132
02:08:38,879 --> 02:08:41,213
It won't be easy getting at him.
He was insulated.

2133
02:08:41,381 --> 02:08:43,132
You'll have to find out how.

2134
02:08:47,095 --> 02:08:50,139
Mitchell started doing covert stuff
before anyone else.

2135
02:08:50,307 --> 02:08:53,726
The list is longer
than anyone can imagine.

2136
02:08:55,562 --> 02:09:00,608
It involves the entire
U.S. intelligence community.

2137
02:09:01,026 --> 02:09:02,151
FBI...

2138
02:09:03,361 --> 02:09:05,487
...CIA, Justice.

2139
02:09:05,655 --> 02:09:07,323
It's incredible.

2140
02:09:09,576 --> 02:09:11,660
The cover-up had little to do
with Watergate.

2141
02:09:11,828 --> 02:09:16,290
It was mainly
to protect the covert operations.

2142
02:09:17,125 --> 02:09:19,001
It leads everywhere.

2143
02:09:22,130 --> 02:09:25,215
Get out your notebook. There's more.

2144
02:09:30,805 --> 02:09:33,557
Your lives are in danger.

2145
02:09:34,392 --> 02:09:37,269
CARL:
Hi. I finally got Sloan on the phone.

2146
02:09:49,157 --> 02:09:51,158
[CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING
OVER SPEAKERS]

2147
02:10:57,058 --> 02:10:58,934
BEN:
Why couldn't you tell me over the phone?

2148
02:10:59,102 --> 02:11:00,936
- Phones aren't safe.
- Can't trust them.

2149
02:11:01,104 --> 02:11:02,813
- Come on in.
BOB: We can't come in, sir.

2150
02:11:02,981 --> 02:11:05,357
CARL: Woodward says
there's electronic surveillance.

2151
02:11:22,625 --> 02:11:24,835
- Surveillance? Who's doing it?
- It's being done.

2152
02:11:25,003 --> 02:11:26,712
- People's lives are in danger.
BEN: Wait.

2153
02:11:26,880 --> 02:11:29,465
- Maybe even ours.
BEN: What happened to that Justice source?

2154
02:11:29,632 --> 02:11:31,508
I made the instructions too complicated.

2155
02:11:31,676 --> 02:11:33,802
He thought I said "hang up,"
I said "hang on."

2156
02:11:33,970 --> 02:11:35,804
- Jesus Christ.
BOB: The story is right.

2157
02:11:35,972 --> 02:11:38,140
Haldeman was the fifth man
to control that fund.

2158
02:11:38,308 --> 02:11:40,809
- Sloan would've told the grand jury.
- Sloan wanted to.

2159
02:11:40,977 --> 02:11:42,978
BEN: Why didn't he?
- Because nobody asked.

2160
02:11:43,897 --> 02:11:46,106
The cover-up had little to do
with the break-in.

2161
02:11:46,274 --> 02:11:48,233
It was to protect covert operations...

2162
02:11:48,401 --> 02:11:50,819
...involving the entire
U.S. intelligence community.

2163
02:11:50,987 --> 02:11:53,489
Did Deep Throat say
that people's lives are in danger?

2164
02:11:53,656 --> 02:11:56,658
- Yes.
- What else did he say?

2165
02:11:57,118 --> 02:11:59,536
He said everyone is involved.

2166
02:12:06,586 --> 02:12:09,171
You know the results
of the latest Gallup poll?

2167
02:12:09,339 --> 02:12:12,007
Half the country never even heard
of the word "Watergate."

2168
02:12:12,175 --> 02:12:14,176
Nobody gives a shit.

2169
02:12:16,471 --> 02:12:18,680
You guys are probably pretty tired, right?

2170
02:12:19,474 --> 02:12:22,226
Well, you should be. Go on home.

2171
02:12:22,393 --> 02:12:25,521
Get a nice hot bath, rest up 15 minutes...

2172
02:12:25,688 --> 02:12:28,357
...then get your asses back in gear.

2173
02:12:28,525 --> 02:12:31,860
We're under a lot of pressure, you know,
and you put us there.

2174
02:12:33,696 --> 02:12:34,947
Nothing's riding on this...

2175
02:12:35,115 --> 02:12:38,117
...except the First Amendment
of the Constitution...

2176
02:12:38,284 --> 02:12:42,246
...freedom of the press,
and maybe the future of the country.

2177
02:12:44,040 --> 02:12:46,208
Not that any of that matters...

2178
02:12:46,376 --> 02:12:50,003
...but if you guys fuck up again,
I'm gonna get mad.

2179
02:12:51,798 --> 02:12:53,382
Good night.

2180
02:13:10,441 --> 02:13:12,442
[TYPEWRITER CLACKING]

2181
02:13:21,077 --> 02:13:22,244
ANNOUNCER [ON TV]:
Now, fellow Americans...

2182
02:13:22,412 --> 02:13:27,875
...the honorable chief justice
will administer the oath of office...

2183
02:13:28,042 --> 02:13:31,086
...to the president
of the United States of America.

2184
02:13:31,254 --> 02:13:33,422
Mr. Chief Justice.

2185
02:13:33,590 --> 02:13:35,591
[MARCHING BAND PLAYING ON TV]

2186
02:13:54,944 --> 02:13:59,031
CHIEF JUSTICE: Mr. President, are you ready
to take the constitutional oath?

2187
02:13:59,199 --> 02:14:03,452
If you will place your left hand
on the Bible and raise your right hand...

2188
02:14:03,620 --> 02:14:05,204
...and please repeat after me:

2189
02:14:05,371 --> 02:14:08,498
I, Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...

2190
02:14:08,666 --> 02:14:10,876
NIXON:
I, Richard Nixon, do solemnly swear...

2191
02:14:11,044 --> 02:14:13,421
CHIEF JUSTICE:... that I
will faithfully execute

2192
02:14:13,422 --> 02:14:15,797
the office of president
of the United States...

2193
02:14:15,965 --> 02:14:17,800
NIXON:... that I will
faithfully execute the

2194
02:14:17,801 --> 02:14:19,635
office of president of
the United States...

2195
02:14:19,802 --> 02:14:22,596
CHIEF JUSTICE:
...and will, to the best of my ability...

2196
02:14:22,764 --> 02:14:24,640
...and will, to the best of my ability...

2197
02:14:24,807 --> 02:14:26,642
CHIEF JUSTICE:
...preserve, protect and defend...

2198
02:14:26,809 --> 02:14:29,144
...the Constitution of the United States...

2199
02:14:29,312 --> 02:14:33,315
...preserve and protect and defend
the Constitution of the United States...

2200
02:14:33,483 --> 02:14:34,816
CHIEF JUSTICE
...so help me God.

2201
02:14:34,984 --> 02:14:37,194
...so help me God.

2202
02:14:37,737 --> 02:14:39,738
[MARCHING BAND PLAYING
"HAIL TO THE CHIEF" ON TV]

2203
02:14:41,783 --> 02:14:43,116
[GUNSHOTS ON TV]

2204
02:14:54,045 --> 02:14:55,587
[GUNSHOTS CONTINUE ON TV]

2205
02:18:11,659 --> 02:18:13,660
[ENGLISH - US - SDH]